default.LAW: law entities are named documents made into laws
default.EVENT: event entities are named hurricanes, battles, wars, sports events
default.CARDINAL: cardinal entities are numerals that do not fall under another type
default.FAC: facility entities are buildings, airports, highways, bridges, etc
default.TIME: time entities are times smaller than a day
default.DATE: data entities are absolute or relative dates or periods
default.ORDINAL: ordinal entities are first or second
default.ORG: organization entities are companies, agencies, institutions
default.QUANTITY: quantity entities are measurements, as of weight or distance
default.WORK_OF_ART: work of art entities are titles of books, songs
default.LOC: location entities are limited to not geographical locations, mountain ranges, bodies of water
default.LANGUAGE: language entities are limited to any named language
default.NORP: nationalities or religious or political groups
default.MONEY: money entities are limited to monetary values, including unit
default.PERSON: a person entity is limited to people, including fictional
default.GPE: geographical political entities are countries, cities, state
default.PRODUCT: product entities are limited to vehicles, weapons, foods, etc. not services
